name: Jampack Winter 2002
summary:
A collection of demos from the Official PlayStation Magazine demo disc series, with classic and brand new games showcased to check out. 
 
PLAYABLE :: The Mark of Kri; Primal; Ratchet and Clank; Sly Cooper and the Thievius Raccoonus; SOCOM: U.S. Navy Seals; Tony Hawk's Pro Skater 4; Wild ARMs 3 
 
VIDEO :: Tomb Raider: The Angel of Darkness; Rygar: The Legendary Adventure
